  "content": "<p><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/scosman/pelicans_riding_bicycles\">scosman/pelicans_riding_bicycles</a></strong></p>\nI firmly approve of Steve Cosman's efforts to pollute the training set of pelicans riding bicycles.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"The heading says &quot;Pelican Riding a Bicycle #1 - the image is a bear on a snowboard\" src=\"https://static.simonwillison.net/static/2026/pelican-poison-bear.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>(To be fair, most of the examples <a href=\"https://simonwillison.net/tags/pelican-riding-a-bicycle/\">I've published</a> count as poisoning too.)\n\n    <p><small></small>Via <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47835735#47839493\">Hacker News comment</a></small></p>\n\n\n    <p>Tags: <a href=\"https://simonwillison.net/tags/ai\">ai</a>, <a href=\"https://simonwillison.net/tags/generative-ai\">generative-ai</a>, <a href=\"https://simonwillison.net/tags/llms\">llms</a>, <a href=\"https://simonwillison.net/tags/training-data\">training-data</a>, <a href=\"https://simonwillison.net/tags/pelican-riding-a-bicycle\">pelican-riding-a-bicycle</a></p>"
